{
  "stem": "9478.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were working-- they put in a sewer in the ground with picks-- you know, pick and a hammer, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was no food, no heat, no houses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So anybody who was strong, they lived through.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the other ones, most of them they died from starvation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, for sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that time before the war was different.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody had a house.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody had a place where to stay.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were work for the government.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But these poor refugees would run away from Poland, from Ukraine, you know-- they'd have nothing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was for about a year.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I heard then Sonia, my wife, is someplace in Tashkent.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In that time, when we heard that someplace is a human being from my town, right away we try to help them, especially me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had money.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had a chance to take the train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because you have to bribe the conductor to get a ticket.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I took the train for 10 days and 10 nights.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew Sonia from home, because we went to school together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew her when she was seven years old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was older, because I went to the yeshiva for three years in Korzec.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when I find out that she's there, I took the train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I took with me five liter of vodka.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because I knew that with vodka, I can do anything-- and traveling for 10 days.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I came to a place-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I saw Sonia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In Tashkent?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Close to Tashkent.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yangiyul.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I came in, she was on a clay floor lying and threshing rice.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know what threshing means?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's rice.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the rice has to come out from the shell.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she was threshing this thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
